pageContext.claim: “For decades, Joe Biden let other countries rip you off and cheat America blind! The only people who've benefited from his policies are himself & his family. He shows up every 4 years, and then goes back to D.C. and caters to his special interests. My only special interest is YOU.”
pageContext.analysis: This is ridiculous over-the-top rhetoric, a smear on hyperdrive.
